description: This penthouse condo offers over 1300sqft of living space, two bedrooms, two full baths, and expansive city views from a large private roof deck, in an incredible location just one block from East Broadway's shops and restaurants. New construction built in 2020, with distinctive design and uncompromising craftsmanship, featuring quartz countertops, maple hardwood flooring, custom trims & lighting, Bosch appliances, and Grohe fixtures. The open concept layout features a large island- the perfect space for entertaining. The king sized primary bedroom includes en-suite bath with walk-in shower, double floating vanity, and bathtub. The second bedroom is generously sized and perfect as a guest room or home office. Direct access roof deck and one deeded garage parking space with EV charger complete this home. Situated in a prime South Boston location, and just minutes from the Seaport and Financial District, this unit offers incredible value for the discerning buyer.
